    echo "CloudToLocalLLM Desktop with Enhanced System Tray Architecture has been installed successfully!"
    echo ""
    echo "ðŸš€ Enhanced Features:"
    echo "  âœ… Independent System Tray Daemon with universal connection management"
    echo "  âœ… Automatic failover between local Ollama and cloud connections"
    echo "  âœ… Separate settings interface for daemon configuration"
    echo "  âœ… Crash isolation between tray daemon and main application"
    echo "  âœ… Auth0 authentication with desktop redirect"
    echo "  âœ… Modern Flutter interface"
    echo ""
    echo "ðŸŽ›ï¸ Starting the Enhanced System:"
    echo "  1. Start tray daemon: systemctl --user enable --now cloudtolocalllm-tray"
